        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1025102325" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4023122221961226504">A round of applause for Cristiane Serruya. The best adult erotic contemporary trilogy I have ever had.<br/>Just a small warning: This has more than sex. This trilogy has a story that should be read in full to be understood. There is pain, angst, sex, love triangle, thriller, mystery, and a lot of meaning in all the scenes (even on the sex scenes). <br/>They are not just there for escapism, they are there to be understood. Each and every one.<br/>(I read it again, yes!)</span>

