              <span id="reviewTextContainer2263894173" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16699193144036866499">Very well written with great storylines and plots. Full of expanse and hotness. Absolutely a box set worth the read.<br/><br/>Great stories with a twists and very enjoyable reads. There are laughs, drama, revenge, passion, emotions, hot scenes, twists and lots of chemistry.<br/><br/>I like the main characters and how they develop. Very captivating from first to last chapter. The author has delivered a box set that is worth the read!<br/><br/>I received a copy of this book and am voluntarily leaving a review.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


